            <div class="how--it--works--left">
                "Enabling Artists with a tool to get their content discovered."
            </div>
            <div class="how--it--works--right">
                <h2 class="how-it-works--title">How it works</h2>
                <h2 class="how-it-works--text">Apollo Now presents an innovative, gamified solution for music discovery
                    and
                    artist engagement. See below for steps on how it works.</h2>
                <ul class="how-it--works--steps">
                    <li class="how--it--works--step">
                        <span class="how--it--works--num">1</span>
                        Link to your current streaming platform
                    </li>
                    <li class="how--it--works--step">
                        <span class="how--it--works--num">2</span>
                        You have to be a paid subscribers to either Apple Music or Spotify.
                    </li>
                    <li class="how--it--works--step">
                        <span class="how--it--works--num">3</span>

                        Begin Listening and Earning
                    </li>
                    <li class="how--it--works--step">
                        <span class="how--it--works--num">4</span>
                        Earn Tokens for listening. Rating the song will earn you an additional token.
                    </li>
                    <li class="how--it--works--step">
                        <span class="how--it--works--num">5</span>
                        Cash out, Gift, or Wager your tokens on the performance of your favorite songs to earn
                        additional tokens.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="try--for--free--btn">
                    <span>Try for Free</span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="25" viewBox="0 0 24 25"
                        fill="none">
                        <path d="M9 18.7131L15 12.7131L9 6.71313" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
